text: Samuel "Sam" Campbell (born 29 September 1944) is an Australian equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1944 births Category:Living people Category:Australian male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Australia Category:Equestrians at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:People from New England (New South Wales)
